Hi Martina, 

Thank you for reaching out to us. 

We have checked the Royal Rehab Volunteers page and it seems that the "We are currently unable to accept applications for volunteering" with orange background section is displaying as it should in Firefox. 

See screenshot in Firefox:


It might not be appearing when you check due to the site's cache. We have cleared the cache on our system. Please clear your browser's cache as well before checking the website and try again.

Let us know how it goes.
